videos.headline: Wilkins' run puts Sun Devils on the board
videos.description: Manny Wilkins rushes 8 yards for a touchdown to give Arizona State a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Herbert finds Mitchell to tie the game
videos.description: Justin Herbert connects with Dillon Mitchell in the end zone to put the Ducks on the board.

videos.headline: Wilkins finds Harry to put Sun Devils ahead
videos.description: Manny Wilkins finds N'Keal Harry for a 3-yard Arizona State touchdown.

videos.headline: Freeman closes Oregon's gap before halftime
videos.description: Royce Freeman runs in from 12 yards out for a Ducks touchdown.

videos.headline: Wilkins TD run extends ASU's lead
videos.description: Manny Wilkins rushes into the end zone to give the Sun Devils a 24-14 lead.

videos.headline: Harvey's 63-yard completion puts ASU in the red zone
videos.description: Manny Wilkins finds Jalen Harvey for 63 yards to put the Sun Devils on the 2-yard line.

videos.headline: Harry drives 47 yards to the red zone
videos.description: Manny Wilkins completes to N'Keal Harry for 47 yards to the Oregon 7-yard line.

videos.headline: Richard's 7-yard run to the end zone
videos.description: Demario Richard runs for a 7-yard touchdown to extend Arizona State's lead.

videos.headline: Herbert finds Johnson in the end zone
videos.description: Justin Herbert connects with Johnny Johnson III for a 20-yard TD to close the gap on the Sun Devils.

videos.headline: Oregon's Brooks-James hauls in a 22-yard TD
videos.description: Justin Herbert completes to Tony Brooks-James in the end zone to close the gap on Arizona State.

videos.headline: Breeland goes 51 yards to put the Ducks in the red zone
videos.description: Justin Herbert completes to Jacob Breeland for 51 yards to put Oregon on Arizona State's 5-yard line.

videos.headline: Herbert sneaks in for a TD
videos.description: Justin Herbert rushes 4 yards for a touchdown to put Oregon in the lead.
